Class Catalog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shopgun.android.sdk.model.Catalog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable, IDealer<Catalog>, IErn<Catalog>, IJson<org.json.JSONObject>, IStore<Catalog>

    public class Catalog
extends java.lang.Object
implements IErn<Catalog>, IJson<org.json.JSONObject>, IDealer<Catalog>, IStore<Catalog>, android.os.Parcelable

    This class is a representation of a catalog as the API v2 exposes it

    More documentation available on via our Catalog Reference documentation, on the engineering blog.
